We start 2023 dancing and working on the 102nd floor of the One World building in New York, doing what we love most, capturing weddings. Thanks to all the Couples who have trusted us in 2022. ✨✨

We are grateful for your confidence in us and are excited to see what 2023 holds for us as we continue to grow and expand our wedding business.

We start the year off with new ideas and new goals, and we believe that the best is yet to come. We are looking forward to new adventures and challenges as we continue to improve and provide top-quality services to our Couples. ❤️

None of this would have been possible without the hard work and dedication of our Team. We are thankful for their contributions and the positive impact they have had on our business.

From the 102nd floor of the One World building, we have a unique perspective on the city and on our 2023 goals; we are ready to take on whatever comes our way in 2023. We are eager to create even more beautiful wedding memories for our Couples and are excited to see what the future holds for us.

Amidst the bustling energy of New York City, we have the perfect haven of serenity and beauty at @620loftgarden with its iconic Saint Patrick’s Cathedral gracing the backdrop, the venue offers a captivating juxtaposition of urban charm and natural elegance.

As @pravjotdhatt and @simrannbhattii walked through the enchanting garden hand in hand it was a moment of respite from the city’s vibrant chaos, where time seemed to stand still.

The meticulous floral arrangements, created by the talented @yamiletheventplanner and @proposal007, added a touch of enchantment to the already breathtaking scenery. Each petal, each color, mirrored this Couple blooming love.

Embraced by the melodious cords of @queensdynamicduo, our hearts were lifted to new heights. It was in this picturesque garden, carefully curated, that this new chapter in their lifes begins.

Thanks so much Uma @chicaffairsandevents for bringing together this team to create a forever memory.

#hamptons #weddingvideography #hamptonswedding #nycvideographer

Capturing the Essence of Sophistication at Blue Hill at Stone Barns ✨✨

Last May, we had the incredible honor of documenting a breathtaking wedding at @bluehillfarm. The courtyard served as the perfect backdrop for the heartfelt ceremony, while the blossom garden transformed into a haven for the enchanting cocktail hour.

As guests arrived, they were greeted by the enchanting melodies of a live string quartet, setting the tone for an unforgettable celebration. But it was the moment they stepped into the reception room, adorned with a flowered aisle by @tincanstudios , that left everyone speechless.

With every step flawlessly planned by the amazing Natalie @nfhsanderson  from @amandasavoryevents, led by the talented Natalie, the wedding day unfolded seamlessly, allowing us to capture every magical moment.

Congratulations to the stunning Couple @megdoee & @sgraziano45, and thank you for entrusting us to capture such an special day. 🎥💍❤️

What an unforgettable experience to be part of “Night at the Empire State Building Holiday Party”!

From meeting Miss New York to walking through the empty hallways of the most iconic building in Manhattan, this experience was unique.

To start, we began with some cocktails, champagne and some hors d’oeuvre followed by an incredible olfactory experience at the @olfactorynyc bar where they customized perfumes for us ✨

And the icing on the cake… getting to the 86th floor where the most chic hot cocoa topped with marshmallow and chocolate cookies were awaiting us to warm us before stepping into the outdoors deck where we were delighted by The Big Apple’s night view from the highs, with @nessa.in.nyc amazing live music session to wrap the experience!

Thanks to @Empirestatebldg for this incredible experience to warm our hearts this Holiday. We feel really fortunate to be part of all this! 🌟
